column5: Leaving tomorrow for Lac Seul & looking for a good & reasonable restaurant to eat breakfast at headeding WEST out of Fort Frances. Thank you! RBF

If you will be eventually heading north towards Kenora I recommend the Log Cabin restaurant in Nestor Falls on the west side of 71. That's about 60-70 miles from FF.Also there's a restaurant on south side of 71 in Emo. About 25 miles west of FF.Both are good but IMHO Log Cabin is better.In FF you will be driving past a Timmy's and a McD's on your left if those work for you.Have a safe trip.
X2 on the log cabin in Nester Falls.
i believe they changed their hours and are not open until 11am

I am pretty sure this is the place they mean, Monique's Lawg Cabin. Phone #1-807-482-2402.They are rated at 4.5 stars and are on highway 71. Do a google search of that name or call them.Hope fishing is good for you. We're heading for the other end of Lac Seul Sunday.
Green's BBQ in Nestor Falls....Great breakfast
called lawg cabin no answer. where is the greens bbq in nestor falls for breakfast? i googled it and canadian haven resort came up. is it part of their property?
